beer.beer_description: Light straw coloured and slightly hazy from the dry hopping, this beer enters the glass building a small but firm snow white head. The aroma is full of citrus with notes of pine needles and hay leading to a light and bright malt profile with hints of wheat toast and mouthcovering hops. The aftertaste is dry with a lingering bitterness.
